{"tid":1872446,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新口罩可能比舊口罩更差","createTime":"2020-02-10T05:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T05:42:22.000Z","uid":301729,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50504d0b6ad31e3d60d93a9901000f725db39a3f","tid":1872446,"uid":301729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"買新口罩要睇清楚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4-lKEzJ95mI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4-lKEzJ95mI&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVQb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=9424c694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4-lKEzJ95mI</a><br />\n<br />\n大多數病毒都帶負電荷，所以外科口罩的過濾層大多是帶正電荷以達致吸附病毒效果。但武漢病毒的刺突是帶正電荷，所以大多數外科口罩的表現可能比想像的差很多！而且新口罩可能比舊口罩或洗過水的口罩更差！"}]}